name: Lingkar Meditasi (Meditation Circle) - Part One: Inhale (Synchronization)
description:
Lingkar Meditasi (Meditation Circle)

I created these audio tracks to accompany your meditation. Any kind of meditation methods are welcome, you have the freedom to choose any of the tracks to start with, but i suggest to follow the track order for the best experience. 

The track started with a BPM synchronization of your current heartbeat rate to your relaxed heartbeat rate. Aeolian, locrian/diatonic minor, and blues scale is used in the making of this audio.

Part One: Inhale (Synchronization)
Part Two: Exhale (Eliminate Negativity)
Part Three: Calm Down
Part Four: Awareness and Focus
Part Five: Gain Improvements
